-----
[[include component:image-block
    name=https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/scp-8582/640px-Shoes%2C_woman%27s%2C_pair_%28AM_1992.160-1%29.jpg |
    caption= You would not look good in SCP-8582.|
    align=right |
    width=20em
